snippet.title: PLANT MALL Indigo% Developer Speedrun 3:32
snippet.description:
This is my speedrun of my game PLANT MALL!
I stopped the timer once Gardener stops walking at the end.
https://cam999.itch.io/plant-mall
Indigo% is making sure you collect all 3 indigo treasures before you end the game.
